{"tid":376132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門將於上午6正改掛八號東北風球","createTime":"2017-08-26T19:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T03:46:15.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ad293bccba1e347622023698946b74593450c5","tid":376132,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T19:56:08.000Z","msg":"熱帶氣旋警告 <br />\n本警告於澳門時間 2017 年 08 月 27 日 03 時 49 分發出。 <br />\n以下為澳門最新之熱帶氣旋警告。 <br />\n澳門現正懸掛 三號風球。 <br />\n即表示熱帶氣旋中心移動，可能引致澳門特別行政區吹強風，風速達每小時 41 至 62 公里，陣風約每小時 110 公里。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於 03:00 時，強烈熱帶風暴&ldquo;帕卡&rdquo;(1714) 集結在澳門東南約 200 公里處﹝約北緯 20.7 度，東經 114.7 度﹞，以時速 30 公里的速度向西北方向移動。 <br />\n<br />\n三號風球仍然懸掛。 <br />\n在 03 時強烈熱帶風暴 &ldquo;帕卡&rdquo; (1714) 集結在本澳東南約 200 公里，大致趨向廣東西岸。 <br />\n預測本澳風力將會增強。 <br />\n將於 08 月 27 日 06 時 00 分改掛八號東北風球。 <br />\n由於橋上風力間中達到強風程度及有陣風，呼籲駕駛人仕注意行車安全，電單車請使用西灣大橋電單車專道進行往返。 <br />\n<br />\n三號風球的安全措施提示： <br />\n所有船隻應駛入避風塘及安全之港口；檢查門窗是否穩固；疏通渠道；留意電視台或電台播出有關之熱帶氣旋消息。"},{"pid":"cabca08e93882169394be86fa3eececdc4ab0986","tid":376132,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c947ed286153a13197305051f13d29efbaec9da","tid":376132,"uid":26721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T20:04:33.000Z","msg":"今次會死幾多件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665f3f43818e1cce4d55c46a5494092ec26faa4e","tid":376132,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488f9a3a9a25f9b85ce7575f3ce2dcde72e73965","tid":376132,"uid":50391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你條仆街係咁回帶"},{"pid":"3e4981ea62b2345f5804cb8b4841476c7ba33cf7","tid":376132,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aeb420ef8b04bfbfb402a85480945f362e2855","tid":376132,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4187949475d896dadb7806a00279043e5b1be0e7","tid":376132,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"caca94c673675bb8dd75db2daed7cf1e3f34623e","tid":376132,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"😁"},{"pid":"a4b483c22026faf6d75fbc8ac57e75d001c6b38c","tid":376132,"uid":157232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caca94c673675bb8dd75db2daed7cf1e3f34623e","tid":376132,"uid":41157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"😁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}